image-gallery/
│
├── index.html       # Main HTML layout of the gallery
├── style.css        # Styling for gallery grid, lightbox, responsiveness
└── script.js        # JS functionality: filtering, lightbox, nav

1. index.html – HTML Tasks :

 Create a div container for the calculator layout

 Add a display (input or div) to show the current expression/result

 Create buttons for digits (0–9) and decimal (.)

 Create operator buttons: +, −, ×, ÷

 Add Clear (C) and Equal (=) buttons

 Structure buttons in a grid layout using semantic elements

2. style.css – CSS Tasks :

 Center the calculator on the screen

 Style the calculator container (e.g. border-radius, shadow)

 Style the display area (font size, alignment, padding)

 Style the buttons with hover effects and click feedback

 Make the layout responsive for smaller screens

 Use CSS Grid or Flexbox for button arrangement

 (Bonus) Add theme colors, transitions, or animations

3. ⚙️ script.js – JavaScript Tasks :

 Implement function to append digits/operators to the display

 Implement function to clear the display

 Implement function to evaluate and show the result

 Handle decimal input correctly

 Handle division by zero and other input errors

 (Bonus) Add support for keyboard input (e.g., Enter, Backspace)

 Prevent multiple operators being entered consecutively

* Bonus (Optional) :

 Add dark/light theme toggle

 Add copy-to-clipboard for results

 Add backspace/delete last digit functionality

 Show live result preview as user types








 

